            <title>[HBASE-4726] RS should close region if it fails to mark it as &apos;OPENED&apos;.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4726</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently if a RS fails to mark a region as &apos;OPENED&apos; it only logs an error. It will leave the region open - this has caused duplicate region assignments in one of our production clusters. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
